epi-USD-sanitationDrinkingWater.def: We measure unsafe sanitation using the number of age-standardized disability-adjusted life-years lost per 100,000 persons (DALY rate) due to their exposure to inadequate sanitation facilities.
epi-USD-sanitationDrinkingWater.name: Unsafe sanitation
epi-USD-sanitationDrinkingWater.source: Institute for Health Metrics and Evaluation

epi-UWD-sanitationDrinkingWater.def: We measure unsafe drinking water using the number of age-standardized disability-adjusted life-years lost per 100,000 persons (DALY rate) due to exposure to unsafe drinking water.
epi-UWD-sanitationDrinkingWater.name: Unsafe Drinking Water
epi-UWD-sanitationDrinkingWater.source: Institute for Health Metrics and Evaluation
